Interface S3ClientMultipartUpload

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AwsS3ClientMultipartUpload, FileMockS3ClientMultipartUpload

    public interface S3ClientMultipartUpload
    Acts as a wrapper around a S3Client, which allows for implementations that could allow for testing or custom behavior.
